{"word":"G4029 - περίκειμαι - períkeimai - per-ik'-i-mahee - Be bound with","slug":"G4029","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περίκειμαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>períkeimai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>per-ik'-i-mahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be bound with"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x0301;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - perikeimai</b> - <i>per-ik'-i-mahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2749\">G2749</a>; to <i>lie</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, <i>inclose</i>, <i>encircle</i>, <i>hamper</i> (literally or figuratively): - be bound (compassed) with, hang about."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1945\">G1945</a>, <a href=\"#/G2621\">G2621</a>, <a href=\"#/G2749\">G2749</a>, <a href=\"#/G345\">G345</a>, <a href=\"#/G3873\">G3873</a>, <a href=\"#/G4295\">G4295</a>, <a href=\"#/G480\">G480</a>, <a href=\"#/G4873\">G4873</a>, <a href=\"#/G606\">G606</a>"}]}